---
import aboutMeImage from '../../../assets/about-me.webp'
import { Mail, Phone } from '@lucide/astro'
---

<section
  id='sobre-mi'
  class='relative overflow-hidden bg-petrol-50 py-24 md:py-32'>


  <!-- Titan One watermark -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -right-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none leading-none'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive; font-size: clamp(10rem, 22vw, 20rem); color: rgba(249,115,22,0.04); line-height: 1;'>
    SEO
  </div>

  <!-- Orange geometric accent -->
  <div
    class='absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-1.5 h-40 bg-orange-500 rounded-r-full pointer-events-none'
    aria-hidden='true'></div>

  <div class='mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8'>
    <div
      data-animate-direction='left'
      class='grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center'>

      <!-- Photo column -->
      <div class='relative flex justify-center lg:justify-start flex-shrink-0'>

        <!-- Stacked background rects for depth -->
        <div
          class='absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full rounded-2xl bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20'
          aria-hidden='true'></div>
        <div
          class='absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-full h-full rounded-2xl bg-sky-500/8 border border-sky-100'
          aria-hidden='true'></div>

        <img
          src={aboutMeImage.src}
          width={aboutMeImage.width}
          height={aboutMeImage.height}
          alt='Salvador Jesús, consultor SEO freelance en Barcelona'
          class='relative aspect-4/5 w-56 sm:w-64 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-2xl shadow-petrol-900/15 ring-1 ring-petrol-900/5'
        />

        <!-- Orange corner dot -->
        <div
          class='absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-orange-500 shadow-sm shadow-orange-500/40'
          aria-hidden='true'></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content column -->
      <div class='space-y-7 max-w-xl'>

        <!-- Eyebrow label -->
        <div class='flex items-center gap-3'>
          <span class='h-px w-8 bg-orange-500 flex-shrink-0'></span>
          <span
            class='text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-orange-500'>
            Sobre mí
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Name + Role -->
        <div class='space-y-1.5'>
          <p
            class='text-4xl sm:text-5xl tracking-tight text-petrol-900'
            style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'>
            Salvador Jesús
          </p>
          <h2 class='text-base font-medium text-sky-600 tracking-wide'>
            Consultor SEO freelance en Barcelona
          </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <p class='text-base/7 text-petrol-700 text-pretty'>
          Vengo del diseño web y la programación frontend. Eso significa que no solo sé qué hay que mejorar en tu web para posicionar, sino que sé cómo hacerlo técnicamente.
        </p>
        <p class='mt-4 text-base/7 text-petrol-700 text-pretty'>
          Trabajo con pocos clientes a la vez.
          <strong class='font-semibold text-petrol-900'>El que lleva tu proyecto soy yo, siempre.</strong>
        </p>

        <!-- Tool badges -->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-2'>
          {
            [
              'Google Search Console',
              'Google Analytics 4',
              'Keyword Planner',
              'WordPress',
              'Elementor Pro',
              'Yoast SEO',
              'DinoRank',
            ].map((tool) => (
              <span class='inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-petrol-700 ring-1 ring-inset ring-petrol-200'>
                {tool}
              </span>
            ))
          }
        </div>

        <hr class='border-petrol-100' />

        <!-- Contact links -->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-4'>
          <a
            href='mailto:salvadorjesus.seo@gmail.com'
            class='group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-petrol-700 hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors duration-200'>
            <span
              class='flex h-9 w-9 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-petrol-50 ring-1 ring-petrol-100 group-hover:bg-sky-50 group-hover:ring-sky-200 transition-all duration-200'>
              <Mail class='h-4 w-4' />
            </span>
            salvadorjesus.seo@gmail.com
          </a>

          <a
            href='tel:+34692051399'
            class='group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-petrol-700 hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors duration-200'>
            <span
              class='flex h-9 w-9 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-petrol-50 ring-1 ring-petrol-100 group-hover:bg-sky-50 group-hover:ring-sky-200 transition-all duration-200'>
              <Phone class='h-4 w-4' />
            </span>
            +34 692 051 399
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
